'From Squeak2.8alpha of 16 February 2000 [latest update: #2246] on 5 June 2000 at 6:27:40 pm'!"Change Set:		ListTypo-arDate:			5 June 2000Author:			Andreas RaabFixes a typo in Smalltalk>>listLoadedModules."!!SystemDictionary methodsFor: 'miscellaneous' stamp: 'ar 6/5/2000 18:26'!listLoadedModules	"Smalltalk listLoadedModules"	"Return a list of all loaded modules (e.g., plugins).	This list is not sorted!!"	| modules index name |	modules _ WriteStream on: Array new.	index _ 1.	[true] whileTrue:[		name _ self listLoadedModule: index.		name ifNil:[^modules contents].		modules nextPut: name.		index _ index + 1.	].! !